If you want to call up the context menu by right clicking, you need to make sure that the mouse has moved to the position on the screen, and then execute the right clicking. Since you do not need to click on specific screen elements, you can right-click anywhere on the screen.
Here is an example JSON action to perform this operation. Select the screen center as the click point:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "right", "mouse_position": {"width": 512, "height": 384}}
]
```
